tables.table_schema:
CREATE TABLE TrainingSession ( 
  session_id UUID PRIMARY KEY, 
  video_url VARCHAR, 
  coach_name VARCHAR, 
  start_time TIMESTAMP, 
  end_time TIMESTAMP, 
  technique_feedback TEXT, 
  performance_feedback TEXT 
)

CREATE TABLE TrainingSessions (
    session_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    session_date DATE,
    session_duration TIME,
    coach_id INT,
    video_url TEXT
);

CREATE TABLE PerformanceFeedback (
    feedback_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    session_id INT,
    technique_id INT,
    feedback TEXT,
    rating INT
);

CREATE TABLE athletes (
    athlete_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    name VARCHAR,
    age INT,
    height FLOAT,
    weight FLOAT
);

CREATE TABLE performance_feedback (
    feedback_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    session_id INT,
    athlete_id INT,
    technique_id INT,
    feedback TEXT
);

CREATE TABLE video_analysis (
    analysis_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    video_url VARCHAR,
    technique_id INT,
    timestamp TIME,
    analysis_result TEXT
);
